GW finally decided to get a decent desktop publisher to make thier new stuff more snazy.  The new book is full of fluff, lots of new wargear to customize the new troops, nothing overboard, but just plain cool stuff.  And the best is bascically Codex Astartes on all the major chapters so far.  The Emperor's Children are bad ass mofo's now!! :)<br>
The only downer is that there is almost no pictures of the models and none of them are the new range to be released.  But you can find those pictures elsewhere.<br>
<br>
Just a side note for Ken. The Word Bearers are still the same as the last update, Undivded, get to take all four types of demons, get an evil Chaplain, and extra troop choices.<br>
<br>
