<br>
Also got to see the new Fantasy Slaanesh general on tit-back when I got my tour around the stock room to see the other chaos stuff.  It is sweet looking.  <br>
<br>
And saw a Monolith put together.  It looks awesome on the battlefield but Nick told me it was a pain in the arse to put together.  The other Necron player also chimed in that the sides are warped out of the box and it takes lots of cursing to get them put together and make look smooth.  But to see that big ole house in action is pretty awesome.  <br>
<br>
Oh, and lastly saw the new deamonettes a staff member was painting up for offical release this weekend.  Ther are pretty much meal ole bitches.  <br>
